# Scooby Project

## 1) Run the Backend

```bash
cd /Users/ericmatamoros/Desktop/Projects/Scooby/backend \
  && source ../venv/bin/activate \
  && pip install -r requirements.txt --upgrade | cat \
  && pkill -f "uvicorn app.main:app" || true; \
  uvicorn app.main:app --reload --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000 | cat
```

## 2) Run the Frontend

```bash
cd /Users/ericmatamoros/Desktop/Projects/Scooby/frontend \
  && npm run dev
```

